Welcome
========================================================
incremental: true

*Statistical Rethinking: A Bayesian Course with Examples in R and Stan*

A joint effort of [Paris Lodron University of Salzburg](https://www.uni-salzburg.at/index.php?id=52) and the [City University of New York Graduate School of Public Health and Health Policy](http://sph.cuny.edu/).

Course will be taught by developing instructors with a focus on using the R language.

Our meetings are open to all (see details below) and our materials are licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International Public License.

We hope you will join our sessions!

