Contributing
========================================================
incremental: true

- Active participation encouraged
- Just add yourself to the schedule
- Read the chapter in the book
- Prepare a summary presentation
- Complete the chapter's exercises
- And present at the weekly meeting

Presentations
========================================================
incremental: true

- All presentations should be authored in the `.Rpres` format
- Templates for every week are available on GitHub, just edit
- Make sure to add your GitHub username and the presentation date

More details on authoring R presentations:

<https://support.rstudio.com/hc/en-us/articles/200486468>.

Exercises
========================================================
incremental: true

